# Compliance Rules Index (HIPAA + GDPR Baseline)

## Scope
- These rules apply to the rewrite codebase under `ctf/`.
- Legacy folders are reference-only during migration unless explicitly opted in.

## Regulatory Baseline
- Enforce strict covered-entity HIPAA posture by default.
- Enforce GDPR baseline across all personal data processing.
- Allow global transfers only with documented safeguards and approved mechanisms.

## Rule Precedence
1. `001-baseline.mdc`
2. Topic modules `002` through `013`
3. `099-rule-authoring-and-change-control.mdc`

If two rules conflict, the stricter privacy/security requirement wins.

