## Usage Contract
- Before shipping any feature, confirm all relevant modules are satisfied.
- For new plugin capabilities (including messaging modules such as Chyme chat), apply baseline plus plugin command overlays.
- Missing policy metadata, legal basis, retention class, or audit path is a release blocker.